---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_CONFIG } from "../../config/site";
---

<Layout title={`企业品牌 | ${SITE_CONFIG.company.name}`}>
  <section class="work-detail">
    <div class="work-detail__container">
      <article class="work-article">
        <header class="work-article__header">
          <h1>企业品牌</h1>
          <div class="work-meta">
            <span class="work-meta__tag">UI/UX设计</span>
            <span class="work-meta__category">科技初创公司</span>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="work-article__content">
          <h2>项目概览</h2>
          <p>
            为快速增长的科技初创公司进行了全面品牌更新。我们构建了一个统一的视觉识别系统，反映了企业的新方向和价值观。
          </p>

          <h2>实施内容</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>标志设计（新制作）</li>
            <li>色彩调色板定义</li>
            <li>字体系统</li>
            <li>品牌指南制作</li>
            <li>网站重新设计</li>
            <li>营销资料设计</li>
            <li>办公环境设计</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>方法</h2>
          <p>我们不仅进行视觉设计，还通过以下流程提升了整个公司的品牌价值：</p>
          <ul>
            <li>与管理层进行品牌战略研讨会</li>
            <li>员工和客户的访谈调查</li>
            <li>竞争对手分析</li>
            <li>品牌定位定义</li>
            <li>全公司员工培训</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>成果</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>品牌认知度提高 150%</li>
            <li>招聘申请增加 2倍</li>
            <li>客户满意度提高 35 分</li>
            <li>新闻发布数增加 5倍</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="work-article__footer">
          <a href="/works/" class="work-back-link">← 返回作品列表</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .work-detail {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--c-bg-secondary);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }

    &__container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .work-article {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 3rem;
    }

    &__header {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border-light);

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--c-text);

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          font-size: 2rem;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
      }
    }

    &__content {
      color: var(--c-text-sub);
      line-height: 1.8;

      p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
        color: var(--c-text);

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
          margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
        }
      }

      ul {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-left: 1.2rem;

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          margin-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        li {
          margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
          font-size: 0.9rem;

          @media (min-width: 768px) {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
          }
        }
      }

      strong {
        color: var(--c-text);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    }

    &__footer {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border-light);

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
      }
    }
  }

  .work-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .work-meta__tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #e8f0ff;
    color: var(--c-primary);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }

  .work-meta__category {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--c-bg);
    color: var(--c-text-sub);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }

  .work-back-link {
    color: var(--c-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s;
    font-size: 0.9rem;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    &:hover {
      color: var(--c-primary-light);
    }
  }
</style>
